---
import Container from "../layouts/container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/page.astro";

const title = "About Me";
const id = "about_me";
---

<Layout content={{ title, id }}>
  <Container content={{ title, id }}>
    <p class="font-mono font-thin text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      I'm Abhinav Merugu, a Software Engineer with a passion for web and mobile
      application development. With 3 years of experience in the field, I am
      currently pursuing my Masters in Computer Science at CSU Chico and have a
      GPA of 3.7.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 font-mono font-thin text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      My expertise lies in web development, where I have strong knowledge of
      React, TypeScript, JavaScript, C++, Python, Redux, GatsbyJS, NextJS,
      Django, REST APIs, ExpressJS, Astro, Jest unit testing, and more. I'm also
      experienced in mobile application development and have knowledge in
      Machine Learning.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 font-mono font-thin text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      My attention to detail and focus on UX and UI design are integral to my
      work, and I strive to create products that are both beautiful and
      functional. I'm a quick learner, adaptable, and am always looking for
      opportunities to grow and improve my skill set. I have earned over 6
      certifications from Interaction Design Foundation, which highlights my
      dedication to learning and staying on top of the latest industry trends.
    </p>

    <div aria-label="resume" class="mt-10 flex items-center">
      <p class="mr-4 font-bold text-gray-700">Resume</p>
      <a
        title="View Resume"
        href="/resume.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="mr-2 rounded-md bg-sky-300 px-4 py-3 text-center text-xl leading-3 hover:scale-105 dark:bg-blue-500"
        ><ion-icon name="eye-outline"></ion-icon></a
      >
      <a
        title="Download Resume"
        href="/resume.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        download="resume_abhinavmerugu"
        class="ml-2 rounded-md bg-emerald-200 px-4 py-3 text-center text-xl leading-3 hover:scale-105 dark:bg-teal-500"
        ><ion-icon name="cloud-download-outline"></ion-icon></a
      >
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
